嗱！呢度有两个乾坤袋，一叠隐身符
Two Magic Bags here, and some invisible stickers

730
00:38:45,916 --> 00:38:48,396
你一贴咗度符喺身，佢就睇唔到你
You're invisible if you stick one on your body

731
00:38:48,396 --> 00:38:50,792
吼佢唔觉意你就一笠笠落佢个头嗰度
Cover him by it when he is not aware

732
00:38:50,792 --> 00:38:52,500
嗱我喺后面掩护你
I'll cover you up from the back

733
00:38:52,833 --> 00:38:54,792
哇！你句对白不〝嬲〞我讲嗰㖞
This is my line!

734
00:38:54,833 --> 00:38:55,792
你同边个讲？
Whom are you talking to?

735
00:38:56,125 --> 00:38:57,125
同佢啰
To him

736
00:38:58,125 --> 00:39:01,542
好呃！等我帮你呢
Let me help you!

737
00:39:01,542 --> 00:39:03,646
冇得顶！你不愧为我好兄弟
That's great! You're my good bro

738
00:39:03,646 --> 00:39:05,125
嗱，你而家出去叫晒啲手足入嚟
Tell all bros to come in

739
00:39:05,167 --> 00:39:06,146
每人俾度符佢
give a magic sticker to each of them

740
00:39:06,146 --> 00:39:07,917
我返去菩提老祖度攞埋个乾坤袋
I go back to get the Magic Bag

741
00:39:08,208 --> 00:39:09,250
夹手夹脚捉妖精
Then we can catch all the devils

742
00:39:09,417 --> 00:39:10,208
冇问题
No problem

743
00:39:10,333 --> 00:39:11,333
好兄弟
Good brother

744
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:15,417
你今日啲眼神好似咁⋯⋯
Your eyes today…

745
00:39:15,417 --> 00:39:16,167
淫吖嘛
Are they seductive?

746
00:39:16,292 --> 00:39:17,125
系
Yes

747
00:39:21,833 --> 00:39:24,208
我实帮你嘅
I will help you

748
00:39:38,167 --> 00:39:40,083
两位请慢用！
Help yourself!

749
00:39:40,542 --> 00:39:42,312
冇办法，为咗帮主吩咐咋
What to do?

750
00:39:42,312 --> 00:39:43,458
你等下
It is Master's order

751
00:39:43,458 --> 00:39:44,875
你等下
You wait a moment

752
00:39:45,083 --> 00:39:45,875
Asst. Master

753
00:39:49,083 --> 00:39:51,062
通知其他人，帮主揾我哋呀
Tell the others, Master is looking for us

754
00:39:51,062 --> 00:39:51,708
Go

755
00:39:58,667 --> 00:39:59,875
Invisible sticker

756
00:40:00,333 --> 00:40:02,042
行啦⋯⋯
Go…

757
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,041
师姐
Sister

758
00:40:08,041 --> 00:40:08,833
OK….

759
00:40:08,917 --> 00:40:11,042
我哋不动声色，睇佢哋想点
Let's keep quiet and see what they want

760
00:40:23,417 --> 00:40:24,000
师妹

761
00:40:24,083 --> 00:40:25,917
饮酒啦！
Sister, drink!

762
00:40:40,042 --> 00:40:41,542
师姐，你都饮
Sister, you drink too

763
00:40:48,208 --> 00:40:49,333
你做咩嘢？
What are you doing?

764
00:40:50,250 --> 00:40:52,375
我有啲醉，瞓阵先
I'm drunk. I wanna sleep

765
00:40:53,125 --> 00:40:54,958
唔使惊，睇唔到㗎
don't be afraid. We're invisible

766
00:40:55,083 --> 00:40:57,667
唔饮得唔好学人饮啦，真失礼
You shouldn't drink so much if you cannot drink

767
00:41:18,083 --> 00:41:19,667
真系睇唔到㖞
We're invisible

768
00:41:19,833 --> 00:41:21,125
你不〝嬲〞都睇唔到嘅啦
You can see nothing all the time

769
00:41:21,250 --> 00:41:21,917
行
Ok!

770
00:41:26,708 --> 00:41:28,208
帮主咁耐都未嚟嘅
Master hasn't come yet

771
00:41:28,333 --> 00:41:29,292
唔知呢
Yes

772
00:41:29,417 --> 00:41:30,917
又话有烧鸡食
You say there is roast chicken

773
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:40,625
行开

774
00:41:40,833 --> 00:41:43,042
帮主！着火啦
Master! It's burning

775
00:41:44,417 --> 00:41:45,250
Don't be naked.

776
00:42:35,125 --> 00:42:36,771
好还钱㖞，靓仔！
Pay me back! Fool!

777
00:42:36,771 --> 00:42:38,167
讲还钱使乜发烂渣？
No need to be like that?

778
00:42:38,167 --> 00:42:39,354
发你唔起呀，借钱唔使还呀？
None of your business, pay me back

779
00:42:39,354 --> 00:42:40,479
讲呀，我几时挣你钱呀？
None of your business, pay me back

780
00:42:40,479 --> 00:42:41,020
When did I borrow money from you

781
00:42:41,020 --> 00:42:42,125
你挣我钱就真
You owe me

782
00:42:42,125 --> 00:42:43,417
我挣你？
I owe you?

783
00:42:43,417 --> 00:42:44,458
你唔记得呢
Don't you remember?

784
00:42:44,833 --> 00:42:45,875
系呀⋯⋯
No….

785
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:47,812
冇记性
You lost your memory

786
00:42:47,812 --> 00:42:50,042
你真系犀利，对唔住呀
Sorry

787
00:43:10,625 --> 00:43:12,292
靓仔，到你好还钱㖞！
You should pay back!

788
00:43:12,542 --> 00:43:13,792
使唔使发咁大烂渣？
No need to be like that

789
00:43:13,792 --> 00:43:14,958
唔还毁你容都得啊
Pay me back, or I'll ruin your face

790
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:17,062
喂，我上个月咪还咗俾你啰
I paid you back last month

791
00:43:17,062 --> 00:43:18,208
还咗？啊系噃，还咗噃
I paid you back last month

792
00:43:18,208 --> 00:43:19,792
Really? Yes, yes

793
00:43:19,792 --> 00:43:22,542
你老了，你冇记性呀
You're old. You lost your memory

794
00:43:22,625 --> 00:43:25,833
算啦，头先又系我唔啱先嘅
Forget it, it's my fault

795
00:43:26,250 --> 00:43:28,667
切咗佢！都煨晒咯
Cut it! Cut it!

796
00:43:29,125 --> 00:43:31,937
香口啲啫！总好过冇
That's better zxa than nothing

797
00:43:31,937 --> 00:43:33,104
明刀明枪同佢炼过！现身啦！兄弟
Fight with him! Bros!

798
00:43:33,104 --> 00:43:34,354
明刀明枪同佢炼过！现身啦！兄弟
Bros, let's go!

799
00:43:34,354 --> 00:43:35,500
系
Yes!

800
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:40,417
两只妖怪出嚟受死
Devils, come out!

801
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:44,625
乾坤袋呢？喂！
Where is the Magic Bag?

802
00:43:45,125 --> 00:43:48,542
乾坤袋喺度，主人，佢哋想陷害你
The Magic Bag is here. They wanna frame you

803
00:43:49,250 --> 00:43:51,667
反骨仔，你出卖我哋
Traitor, you betray me

804
00:43:55,167 --> 00:43:56,792
不过今日出卖得我
Today, you betray me

805
00:43:56,792 --> 00:43:58,292
听日一样可以出卖番你
I will betray you one day

806
00:43:58,667 --> 00:43:59,708
系咩？
Really?

807
00:43:59,792 --> 00:44:01,000
系呀！
Yes!

808
00:44:04,708 --> 00:44:06,917
我菩提老祖为咗伏妖除魔
I want to destroy all devils

809
00:44:06,917 --> 00:44:08,542
除咗条底裤都要啦
I can take off my underwear!

810
00:44:12,250 --> 00:44:15,375
帮主果然够眼光，二当家真系有问题
Master, there's really something wrong with Asst. Master

811
00:44:15,542 --> 00:44:17,625
平时条友使吓佢做嘢，梗推三推四嘅
That guy is unwilling to do anything even if I beg him

812
00:44:17,833 --> 00:44:19,667
今次咁顺摊，梗有〝景轰〞啦
Now, he admit so quickly. There must be something wrong

813
00:44:19,958 --> 00:44:20,667
拖佢出嚟
Pull him out

814
00:44:20,833 --> 00:44:21,708
系
Yes!

815
00:44:22,583 --> 00:44:23,583
行，⋯⋯行呀

816
00:44:23,708 --> 00:44:24,916
放咗我
Let me go…

817
00:44:24,916 --> 00:44:25,417
放咗我

818
00:44:25,917 --> 00:44:26,667
Let me go

819
00:44:26,958 --> 00:44:28,541
放咗我　　快啲
Shut up

820
00:44:28,541 --> 00:44:30,125
放咗我　　快啲
Let me go

821
00:44:30,333 --> 00:44:31,750
跪低
Kneel down

822
00:44:32,000 --> 00:44:35,167
你条〝沐契〞，今晚我就劏咗你当烧猪食
You son of a bitch, I'm gonna kill you tonight

823
00:44:35,292 --> 00:44:36,792
好！
Fine!

824
00:44:37,333 --> 00:44:38,958
咁又唔怪得佢嘅
You can't blame him

825
00:44:38,958 --> 00:44:42,417
佢不过系受咗嗰两个妖女嘅移魂大法啫
He's only mesmerized by both devils

826
00:44:43,000 --> 00:44:43,833
放咗我！
Let me go

827
00:44:43,958 --> 00:44:45,542
如果唔系我叫我主人杀咗你哋
or I'll tell my Master to kill you

828
00:44:45,625 --> 00:44:47,042
仲驳嘴你
Shut up!

829
00:44:49,375 --> 00:44:50,417
旺财
Wong Choi

830
00:44:50,917 --> 00:44:53,729
乜你咬住条绳好似咁面善咁嘅？
The string you're biting is so familiar

831
00:44:53,729 --> 00:44:54,125
Stranger

832
00:44:54,125 --> 00:44:56,917
咪系我绑乾坤袋条绳嚟啰
It is the string for my Magic Bag

833
00:44:59,708 --> 00:45:00,625
Son of a bitch

834
00:45:00,917 --> 00:45:02,917
死老鬼
How dare you come here!

835
00:45:02,917 --> 00:45:04,917
天堂有路你唔走，地狱无门闯进来
How dare you come here!

836
00:45:05,625 --> 00:45:06,625
嚟吖！
Come here!

837
00:45:06,958 --> 00:45:08,875
等我炼死你个托世孙悟空
I'll kill you, reincarnated Monkey King

838
00:45:08,875 --> 00:45:10,958
你就永远都揾唔到唐三藏㗎嘞
Then you won't find the Longevity Monk

839
00:45:11,625 --> 00:45:12,458
咩话？
What?

840
00:45:12,708 --> 00:45:13,666
佢系孙悟空？
He is the Monkey King?

841
00:45:13,666 --> 00:45:14,625
嚟吖！
He is the Monkey King?

842
00:45:14,917 --> 00:45:16,583
快啲认孙悟空吖
Say you're the Monkey King

843
00:45:16,583 --> 00:45:18,292
唔系就一镬熟㗎嘞
or we'll all die

844
00:45:18,458 --> 00:45:19,333
佢唔系孙悟空！
He's not the Monkey King

845
00:45:19,625 --> 00:45:21,167
佢连我三味白骨火都顶唔住
He can't even withstand my Skeleton Fire

846
00:45:21,292 --> 00:45:22,417
点会系孙悟空吖！
He is not the Monkey King

847
00:45:22,583 --> 00:45:23,916
岂有此理！咁嘅天机你都泄露出嚟嘅
Shit!

848
00:45:23,916 --> 00:45:25,250
岂有此理！咁嘅天机你都泄露出嚟嘅
You've exposed a top secret

849
00:45:25,292 --> 00:45:26,167
系咪？
Really?

850
00:45:26,292 --> 00:45:27,625
呢便呀
This way

851
00:45:27,875 --> 00:45:29,417
你仲算系神仙嚟嘅你
Are you really a fairy?

852
00:45:29,708 --> 00:45:30,708
攞只手嚟吖
Give me your hand

853
00:45:31,167 --> 00:45:33,167
过⋯份⋯呀你
It is too much of you…

854
00:45:33,667 --> 00:45:35,542
你以为我真系怕你三味白骨火呀？
Do you think I can't withstand your Skeleton Fire?

855
00:45:35,792 --> 00:45:37,208
你再烧多一次睇吓
Burn me again

856
00:45:37,333 --> 00:45:38,250
唔系呀？
Serious?

857
00:45:38,667 --> 00:45:40,375
好呀！嘿
Great!

858
00:45:42,167 --> 00:45:44,458
我唔怕嘞！系咪呀！？
I'm not scared! See?

859
00:45:44,667 --> 00:45:45,958
系噃！
Yes!

860
00:45:50,542 --> 00:45:52,958
我孙悟空就一路摆只手喺度俾你烧
You can burn my hand if you like

861
00:45:53,625 --> 00:45:55,542
惊都未惊过呀！
I'm not afraid of you

862
00:45:56,542 --> 00:45:58,833
都唔怕笑死人
Not burn my hand?

863
00:46:05,625 --> 00:46:07,042
煨嘞
Burning

864
00:46:09,958 --> 00:46:12,167
真系烧到㶶晒都冇事㖞
The hand is still OK

865
00:46:13,375 --> 00:46:14,500
放手！
Let go!

866
00:46:15,542 --> 00:46:17,000
而家知我坚㗎啦
Now you know I'm great

867
00:46:17,125 --> 00:46:18,042
好投降啦
Surrender!

868
00:46:18,125 --> 00:46:20,354
我仲有成班兄弟，再加个神仙
I have got my bros and a fairy

869
00:46:20,354 --> 00:46:21,375
喂，你去边呀？
Where are you going?

870
00:46:21,500 --> 00:46:23,208
第日我会同你报仇㗎嘞
I'll take revenge on you one day

871
00:46:23,417 --> 00:46:24,958
哗！连神仙都咁冇义气
Even a fairy is not righteous

872
00:46:25,125 --> 00:46:25,875
咁唔使问啦
No need to ask

873
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:28,042
我成班兄弟梗过晒嗰边啦
My bros must be there

874
00:46:28,417 --> 00:46:30,417
系呀！帮主！
Yes! Master!

875
00:46:30,833 --> 00:46:33,042
呢班契弟
Sons of bitches!

876
00:46:33,792 --> 00:46:35,125
你就喺嗰个负心人？
Are you that heartless guy?

877
00:46:35,458 --> 00:46:36,625
你琴晚仲呃我！
You deceived me last night!

878
00:46:38,083 --> 00:46:39,542
咪就系嗰只马骝精啰
That Monkey King

879
00:46:39,667 --> 00:46:41,854
师妹嫁唔出，都因为你啫
Sister will not be married just because of you

880
00:46:41,854 --> 00:46:42,667
Me?

881
00:46:45,042 --> 00:46:46,167
捉住至尊宝！
Get the Joker!

882
00:46:46,292 --> 00:46:47,208
上
Go!

883
00:46:47,458 --> 00:46:48,458
咪嚟啦
Stop that

884
00:46:48,792 --> 00:46:50,250
帮主走呀
Master, go

885
00:46:59,375 --> 00:47:01,083
唔好杀我啲兄弟啊！
Don't kill my bros!

886
00:47:23,500 --> 00:47:24,500
帮主！
Master

887
00:47:31,417 --> 00:47:33,167
有我喺度唔使怕，盲炳
Blindy, I'm here, no need to scare me

888
00:47:36,375 --> 00:47:37,375
对唔住，盲炳
Sorry, Blindy!

889
00:47:37,542 --> 00:47:38,625
计错数，行少咗一步
You have made a mistake

890
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:40,145
你唔会怪我吖嘛？
You won't blame me, will you?

891
00:47:40,145 --> 00:47:43,375
我呢一世人都盲累累做人　　我知
For my whole life I know

892
00:47:43,583 --> 00:47:45,104
最有眼光⋯⋯
I'm blind…

893
00:47:45,104 --> 00:47:50,042
就系跟住帮主你喇！
But I am right to be your follower!

894
00:47:53,542 --> 00:47:55,292
同你搏命！
Kill you!

895
00:47:59,208 --> 00:48:00,395
死过未你
You go to hell

896
00:48:00,395 --> 00:48:01,520
唔舍得杀个负心人
You can't kill him

897
00:48:01,520 --> 00:48:02,667
你仲帮住佢
You still help him

898
00:48:02,667 --> 00:48:03,875
仲要靠佢揾唐僧
You want to rely on him to find the Longevity Monk

899
00:48:04,167 --> 00:48:05,625
带番盘丝洞
Take him back to Spider's Web Cave

900
00:48:09,667 --> 00:48:10,542
师姐
Sister

901
00:48:11,625 --> 00:48:14,833
一个和尚担水食，两个和尚冇水食
Only one man can benefit from it

902
00:48:15,042 --> 00:48:16,708
原来呢个道理你唔明
You don't know this in fact

903
00:48:17,417 --> 00:48:19,458
你打伤咗我，都唔见得一定有水食吖
You won't gain anything even if you hurt me

904
00:48:19,625 --> 00:48:20,917
睇吓你自己只掌
Look at your palm

905
00:48:22,042 --> 00:48:23,375
吓！黑寡妇
Black Widow!

906
00:48:25,417 --> 00:48:27,000
你中咗我盘丝软甲嘅毒
You've been poisoned by my weapon

907
00:48:27,208 --> 00:48:28,542
七日之内如果冇我嘅解药
You will die in 7 days

908
00:48:28,708 --> 00:48:30,292
你就会毒发攻心而死
if you can't get my remedy

909
00:48:31,375 --> 00:48:33,125
师姐，我以后唔敢啦
Sister, I don't dare to do so anymore

910
00:48:33,167 --> 00:48:34,208
躝开！
Get lost!

911
00:48:38,042 --> 00:48:40,000
终于都良心发现啦你
You regret at last

912
00:48:40,167 --> 00:48:42,625
唔系呀！　出面嚟咗只猛嘢呀
No! A fierce thing has come

913
00:48:44,250 --> 00:48:45,167
出去睇吓
Go out and have a look

914
00:48:47,167 --> 00:48:48,292
你哋去边呀？
Where are you going?

915
00:48:48,500 --> 00:48:49,292
唔好呀！⋯
No!…

916
00:48:53,917 --> 00:48:55,292
牛魔王都嚟咗？
King Bull has come?

917
00:48:55,792 --> 00:48:58,917
King Bull?

918
00:49:04,917 --> 00:49:06,125
嚟呢度诈死呀？
Pretend to be dead here?

919
00:49:06,208 --> 00:49:06,958
我都话你嚟⋯⋯
Me too…

920
00:49:08,458 --> 00:49:10,875
开刀吖
Monster

921
00:49:14,333 --> 00:49:15,208
快啲走吖，走吖

922
00:49:21,583 --> 00:49:22,792
菩提老祖
Grandpa Buddha

923
00:49:23,208 --> 00:49:25,042
今日你唔将唐三藏交出嚟
Give the Longevity Monk to me

924
00:49:25,292 --> 00:49:26,208
就死路一条
or you're gonna die

925
00:49:26,333 --> 00:49:27,208
你同我讲咁多做咩啫？
